2Ô∏è‚É£ QUESTION & ANSWER PAGES
2.1 Q&A Page (Community Driven)
Use when
ONE question
Users submit answers
Voting / accepted answer exists
Schema
QAPage
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "QAPage",
  "mainEntity": {
    "@type": "Question",
    "name": "How does Redis help JWT authentication?",
    "text": "Why is Redis used with JWT tokens?",
    "answerCount": 1,
    "acceptedAnswer": {
      "@type": "Answer",
      "text": "Redis helps by storing token blacklists and session metadata."
    }
  }
}
2.2 FAQ Page (Publisher Driven)
Use when
Multiple questions
Answers written by site owner
No user interaction
Schema
FAQPage
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "FAQPage",
  "mainEntity": [
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "What is JWT?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "JWT is a stateless authentication token."
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Is JWT secure?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "Yes, if implemented correctly."
      }
    }
  ]
}
